        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/kamil-al-ziyarat:2:58:6",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/24/2/58/6",
        "text": [
          " حَدَّثَنَا سَالِمٌ أَبُو سَلَمَةَ وَ هُوَ أَبُو خَدِيجَةَ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ (ع) قَالَ إِنَّ زِيَارَةَ الْحُسَيْنِ (ع) أَفْضَلُ مَا يَكُونُ مِنَ الْأَعْمَالِ"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayyid-mohsen-al-husayni-al-milani": [
            "6. Muḥammad ibn Ja’far Al-Razzāz narrated to me from Muḥammad ibn Ḥusain, from ‘Abdil Raḥmān ibn Abī Hāshim Al-Razzāz, from Abī Salamah Sālim – referring to Abī Khadījah, who said: Abū ‘Abdillāh (Imam Sādiq (a.s.)) said: Verily the Ziyārah of Ḥusain (a.s.) is the best of deeds."
          ]
        }
      }
